<p><img src="/media/13086966/site_masthead_chalet.jpg" alt="Inghams Chalets" data-udi="umb://media/dfaefa21358048d88db8a58b5b65a72a" /></p>
<h2>Catered ski chalets</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Our catered ski chalets are the perfect base for your alpine holiday. Your chalet hosts will be ready to help you with all aspects of your holiday, ready to make your stay as comfortable as possible.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">You can expect plenty of home-cooked comfort food to fuel your ski days, so all you have to do is get up and go skiing. As well as preparing and serving meals, your host will also clean-up and make beds for you. After all, you're on holiday!</span></p>
<h3>A home-from-home environment</h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Cosy with warm and welcoming furnishings and décor, our ski chalets feature all the comforts of home. Full of thoughtful touches, each chalet boasts an inviting atmosphere and plenty of space to relax after a day on the slopes. You’ll be able to enjoy breakfast, afternoon tea and dinner every day while you take in stunning mountain views from your very own private balcony or terrace.</span></p>
